fields.name: Chocolate Cake
fields.description: A rich and moist chocolate cake with layers of chocolate ganache, covers in fresh fruits.

fields.name: Vanilla Cake
fields.description: A classic vanilla cake with buttercream frosting, decorated with fresh flowers.

fields.name: Sponge Cake
fields.description: A three-layered sponge cake, filled with creamy mass, adorned with fresh fruits and edible flowers.

fields.name: Lemon Cake
fields.description: A Refreshing lemon-flavoured cake on crispy base, decorated with lemon cream and fresh strawberries.

fields.name: Underwater adventure
fields.description: This perfect party cake is a celebration of all things fun! This two-layered cake is inspired by amazing underwater adventures from books for our youngest, decorated with fully edible water creatures

fields.name: Teddy Bear
fields.description: A beautiful three-tier birthday cake straight from childhood dreams. Each tier is meticulously crafted with vibrant colors and intricate details, creating a visually captivating and delicious treat.

fields.name: Cherry Cake
fields.description: This Dream Cake is a refreshing combination of yummy cherry compote, zesty buttercream, custard, crispy pearls, digestive crumb and moist rum infused sponge.

fields.name: Rainbow cake
fields.description: A six-layered, multicoloured sponge, made with only natural colourings is filled, covered and decorated with smooth vanilla buttercream.

fields.name: Elegant Delight
fields.description: We are in love with this elegant wedding cake. Our newest design and now a bestseller, this modern wedding cake has a soft, vanilla buttercream and your choice of a decorations such a flowers and toppers

fields.name: Celestial Surprise
fields.description: It is a whimsical cake that captures the joy of opening presents. The flavour of the cake is a delectable combination of vanilla and strawberry, creating a delightful balance of sweetness. The layers are generously filled with a luscious strawberry cream, complemented by a light vanilla buttercream frosting.

fields.name: Cherry Chocolate Delight
fields.description: It is a delectable blue cake adorned with luscious cherries and rich chocolate. The cake is moist and fluffy, with a vibrant blue hue that adds an eye-catching appeal. It is layered with a velvety chocolate ganache and filled with a delightful cherry compote. The cake is further enhanced with a smooth buttercream frosting, elegantly piped with intricate designs.

fields.name: Decadent Chocolate Truffle Cake
fields.description: This rich and indulgent dessert features a moist chocolate cake base, generously frosted with a velvety chocolate ganache. The cake is adorned with luscious chocolate truffles on top, adding an extra layer of chocolatey goodness.

fields.name: Floral Delight Cake
fields.description: The Floral Delight Cake is an exquisite creation that combines the artistry of flowers with the indulgence of cake. The cake is composed of moist layers with a tender crumb, delicately flavored with vanilla. The frosting is a smooth and creamy buttercream, providing a luscious base for the floral decorations. Adorning the top of the cake are an assortment of edible flowers, carefully arranged to create a visually stunning display.

fields.name: Elegant Noir
fields.description: The 'Elegant Noir' cake is a stunning black and gold birthday cake. This exquisite confection features multiple tiers, each meticulously decorated to create a luxurious and elegant aesthetic. The cake is covered in smooth, jet-black fondant, which serves as the perfect canvas to showcase the intricate golden details. Delicate gold filigree patterns adorn the sides of each tier, adding a touch of opulence and sophistication.

fields.name: Colorful Candy Cake
fields.description: It is a rich and moist chocolate cake that is sure to satisfy your sweet tooth. It is beautifully decorated with an assortment of colorful candies, adding a playful and festive touch. The cake is further enhanced with candles, making it perfect for birthday celebrations.

fields.name: Joyful Celebration Cake
fields.description: It is a delightful creation perfect for birthdays and special occasions. This scrumptious cake features layers of moist vanilla sponge cake filled with a luscious raspberry cream and frosted with a velvety Swiss meringue buttercream. Adorned with vibrant rainbow sprinkles, this cake is guaranteed to bring smiles to everyone's faces. The finishing touch is a whimsical decoration of fondant flowers and a whimsical chocolate topper, making it an enchanting centerpiece for any celebration.

fields.name: Sweet Teddy Delight
fields.description: 'The Sweet Teddy Delight' is a delightful creation that combines the irresistible flavors of pink and white in a visually stunning cake. This cake is perfect for any special occasion, be it a birthday, baby shower, or simply a celebration of sweetness.

fields.name: Berry Bliss Cake
fields.description: The Berry Bliss Cake is a delightful white cake adorned with a vibrant assortment of fresh berries on top. This visually stunning cake combines the lightness of the white cake with the natural sweetness and tartness of the berries, creating a harmonious balance of flavours.

fields.name: Blossoming Elegance
fields.description: The 'Blossoming Elegance' cake is a delightful creation that combines the simplicity of a white cake with the delicate beauty of pink flowers. It is a true feast for the eyes and the taste buds.This exquisite cake features a light and fluffy white sponge base, perfectly moistened with a hint of vanilla essence. The cake layers are generously filled with a luscious strawberry cream, adding a burst of fruity flavor to each bite.

fields.name: Pink Champagne Delight
fields.description: The 'Pink Champagne Delight' is a stunning wedding cake that exudes elegance and sophistication. It features multiple tiers adorned with intricate pink and gold designs, creating a harmonious blend of colors. The cake is made with a moist and fluffy champagne-infused sponge, which adds a subtle hint of sophistication to each bite. The layers of the cake are filled with a luscious raspberry mousse, adding a burst of fruity flavor that complements the champagne undertones perfectly. Between each layer, a delicate champagne-infused buttercream frosting is spread, adding a light and creamy texture to the cake.

fields.name: Berry Bliss Wedding Cake
fields.description: It is a delightful creation that combines the elegance of a traditional wedding cake with the vibrant flavors of fresh berries. This stunning two-tiered cake is adorned with a luscious array of strawberries and berries on top, creating a visually appealing and mouthwatering treat for the special occasion.

fields.name: Blushing Elegance
fields.description: The 'Blushing Elegance' wedding cake is a stunning masterpiece that combines the timeless elegance of pink and gold. This four-tiered cake stands tall on a beautifully adorned table, ready to mesmerize guests with its exquisite design. The cake features a smooth, pale pink buttercream frosting that creates a soft and romantic ambiance. Delicate gold accents, meticulously hand-piped, gracefully adorn each tier, adding a touch of opulence and sophistication.

fields.name: Frosty Elegance
fields.description: The 'Frosty Elegance' wedding cake is a stunning confection that exudes timeless beauty. This three-tiered masterpiece features a white base, meticulously crafted with layers of moist vanilla cake. The delicate blue flowers adorning the top of the cake are handcrafted from sugar paste and provide a captivating touch of color.

fields.name: Celestial Bliss Cake
fields.description: The Celestial Bliss Cake is an exquisite creation designed to add elegance and charm to any wedding celebration. This stunning cake features multiple tiers adorned with delicate white and blue decorations, symbolizing purity and serenity.

fields.name: Triple Chocolate Delight Cupcake
fields.description: The Triple Chocolate Delight Cupcake is a decadent treat that combines the rich flavors of three different types of chocolate. This indulgent cupcake features a moist chocolate base infused with cocoa powder and melted dark chocolate. Topped with a luscious chocolate ganache frosting, each bite is a heavenly experience. To add a delightful texture, the cupcake is garnished with chocolate shavings and a sprinkle of cocoa powder.

fields.name: Raspberry Chocolate Delight Cupcakes
fields.description: These delectable Raspberry Chocolate Delight Cupcakes are a perfect combination of rich, velvety chocolate and tangy raspberry flavors. The moist chocolate cupcake base is infused with cocoa powder and topped with a luscious raspberry buttercream frosting. Each bite is a harmonious balance of sweet and tart, melting in your mouth and leaving you craving for more.

fields.name: Almond Brownies
fields.description: Almond Brownies are a delectable treat that combines the rich, fudgy goodness of chocolate brownies with the delightful crunch of almonds. These indulgent brownies are made with a moist and dense chocolate base, generously studded with chopped almonds, and topped with a layer of whole almonds for an irresistible presentation.

fields.name: Spooky Delight Cupcake
fields.description: These Spooky Delight Cupcakes are the perfect treat for Halloween festivities! Each cupcake is adorned with a delicious combination of flavors and decorations that will delight both kids and adults alike.

fields.name: Blueberry Bliss Brownie
fields.description: The Blueberry Bliss Brownie is a delectable treat that combines the rich, indulgent flavors of a classic chocolate brownie with the vibrant burst of fresh blueberries. This heavenly dessert features a fudgy and moist chocolate brownie base, generously studded with juicy blueberries throughout. The brownie is perfectly baked to achieve a soft and gooey texture, while the blueberries add a delightful tangy sweetness that complements the rich chocolate perfectly.

fields.name: Decadent Delight Brownie
fields.description: The Decadent Delight Brownie is crafted with a combination of high-quality ingredients to create the perfect balance of flavors. The main ingredients include premium dark chocolate, unsalted butter, granulated sugar, eggs, all-purpose flour, cocoa powder, and a touch of vanilla extract.
